N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 4051.1 - All meetings must be sanctioned

State Regulations

All meetings given by hunt clubs and similar
organizations must be sanctioned by the hunts committee. The list of officials
for such meetings and the program for the same must be submitted for approval
to the hunts committee. Notes
